1
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:35,000
[Truth or Dare - Episode 30]

2
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:37,400
[Blooming Flowers and a Full Moon]
(T/N: idiom for Marital Bliss)

3
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:39,800
Bestow Xiao Bao with a family name.

4
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:41,700
If Your Highness bestows me with a family name,

5
00:01:41,700 --> 00:01:45,000
it's really a blessing that I can't cultivate for three lives.

6
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,800
What a bold thief.

7
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:49,800
Ninth Prince Manor is not a place you can seek connections with.

8
00:01:51,800 --> 00:01:52,800
Someone!

9
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:55,800
Capture this mountain bandit who's guilty of evil crimes.

10
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:58,000
Father, what are you trying to do?

11
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:05,500
You may be muddle-headed but I will not be muddle-headed with you.

12
00:02:05,500 --> 00:02:07,400
You can't ruin your future because of them

13
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:09,300
and ruin the entire Ninth Prince Manor!

14
00:02:09,300 --> 00:02:10,800
Them?

15
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:13,800
Are you going to capture Xiao Wanzi, too?

16
00:02:18,600 --> 00:02:21,200
Why are they still not back yet?

17
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:36,700
Young Master, I was late to escorting the princess and Master Xiao Bao.

18
00:02:36,700 --> 00:02:39,900
I didn't do my job well and, thus, attracted trouble.

19
00:02:41,260 --> 00:02:42,970
This is not your fault.

20
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:47,890
Are you worried that Ninth Prince won't easily give this a rest?

21
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:51,600
I was thinking it is very suspicious of Ninth Prince

22
00:02:51,600 --> 00:02:54,800
to suddenly summon us to the capital.

23
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:56,400
Suspicious?

24
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:59,600
Although the Salt Gang has been eliminated, all the clues

25
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:01,800
point towards the court and people of the capital.

26
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:05,400
This has already dragged everyone into this muddled business.

27
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:07,600
Young Master, are you saying

28
00:03:07,600 --> 00:03:11,200
that the emperor has summoned you in regards to the Salt Gang?

29
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:13,000
Before, A'Rou found out that

30
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:16,700
a sum of money flowed to Fu Longchang.

31
00:03:16,700 --> 00:03:21,600
Regardless of who is here in the capital, we need to act first in order to gain the upper hand.

32
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:23,400
Understood.

33
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:26,800
Go to Fu Longchang to arrest Dong Daman immediately.

34
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:28,800
Young Master, don't worry.

35
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:31,200
I will definitely find the truth behind all this.

36
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,600
What are you all doing?

37
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:36,000
As expected.

38
00:03:37,200 --> 00:03:39,800
Shiqing! Shiqing, they want to take me!

39
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:42,400
Shiqing!

40
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:45,700
Prince Consort,

41
00:03:45,700 --> 00:03:47,800
don't give me a hard time.

42
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,600
I'm under orders to do this.

43
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:53,200
If you want to take her, you can. Just take me as well.

44
00:03:53,200 --> 00:03:55,300
Are you crazy, Shiqing?

45
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:59,400
Fine. I will listen to you then. Capture both of them.

46
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:01,100
Yes.

47
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,600
What are you doing?

48
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:16,000
Shiqing.

49
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:23,000
Third Young Master, you are locked up here, too?

50
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:25,200
Are you an idiot?

51
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:28,000
Why did you come to prison with me?

52
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:30,600
Don't worry. I'm here.

53
00:04:32,300 --> 00:04:34,900
Right now, I'm worried about my Yao Yao.

54
00:04:34,900 --> 00:04:39,100
She's out there alone. Who knows what her father will force her to do?

55
00:04:39,900 --> 00:04:41,300
Yao Yao!

56
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:46,100
Yao Yao, why are you here, too?

57
00:04:46,100 --> 00:04:48,400
Your father is too cruel.

58
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:50,600
I asked to be here.

59
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:54,200
I think it's safer for us to be together.

60
00:04:54,200 --> 00:04:58,600
Since the princess has decided, let's live and die together.

61
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:01,900
All right.

62
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:24,800
Damn!

63
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:57,600
It's you, Brother Situ.

64
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:01,900
I thought I encountered some bad people.

65
00:06:01,900 --> 00:06:04,600
Is there any arrangement from the people above us?

66
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:08,600
Hence, you knocked them unconscious as you are afraid they will overhear.

67
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:12,200
Do you know what happened in Qingzhou?

68
00:06:12,200 --> 00:06:13,800
Master is very troubled.

69
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:17,800
He wants you to close down Fu Longchang for now.

70
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:18,800
Close it?

71
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:21,600
Then... where will I go?

72
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:25,400
Master has ordered you to leave the capital immediately.

73
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:27,600
The farther you go, the better.

74
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:29,800
Understood! Understood.

75
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:33,200
It's a critical time, right? I will leave right away.

76
00:06:34,900 --> 00:06:37,500
I have to see you off

77
00:06:37,500 --> 00:06:40,700
so I can report back.

78
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,600
You...

79
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:50,000
Brother Daman, have a good journey.

80
00:07:11,400 --> 00:07:13,600
Dong Daman! Dong Daman!

81
00:07:14,500 --> 00:07:17,800
Damn. I'm still one step behind.

82
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:42,100
[Master]

83
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:54,800
How did it go?

84
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:58,200
Reporting Prince. Dong Daman is already on his way.

85
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:04,400
I failed to do well regarding things in Qingzhou.

86
00:08:04,400 --> 00:08:06,400
Please punish me.

87
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:09,800
You are still too young and have no foresight.

88
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:13,000
You do not understand the principle of

89
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:16,000
immediately clearing the weeds.

90
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:18,200
Yes. You are right in your teachings.

91
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:21,000
I watched you grow up.

92
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:23,000
After all, your father, Li Tianlong,

93
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:27,000
worked for me in the past.

94
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:30,500
It is a pity that Third Young Master Mei is now at the Ninth Prince Manor.

95
00:08:30,500 --> 00:08:34,000
Even so, I'm willing to kill him for you.

96
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:37,800
It's unnecessary to use a bull-slaughtering knife to kill a chicken.
 (T/N: No need to use great efforts to complete an easy task.)

97
00:08:37,800 --> 00:08:41,400
They are here in the capital now because of my strategy

98
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:45,000
in praising Third Young Master Mei for wiping out

99
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:47,500
the Salt Gang

100
00:08:47,500 --> 00:08:51,200
after his marriage to the princess.

101
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:55,800
The emperor is ecstatic so he wanted to see them.

102
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:57,600
But I heard from the spy that

103
00:08:57,600 --> 00:09:00,600
the real Lu Yingyao has returned to Ninth Prince Manor.

104
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:04,400
Young Master Mei won't that be foolish enough to bring the fake princess to His Majesty, right?

105
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:07,600
As long as there are rumors about a fake princess

106
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:09,400
and I deliver the rumors

107
00:09:09,400 --> 00:09:12,400
to His Majesty, it's enough.

108
00:09:12,400 --> 00:09:16,000
I'm stupid. Prince, please be specific.

109
00:09:16,900 --> 00:09:20,100
Once His Majesty hears that the Mei Manor

110
00:09:20,100 --> 00:09:24,200
allowed the princess to be trapped in the mountain fort

111
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:28,400
and someone to impersonate her,

112
00:09:28,400 --> 00:09:30,830
he will become furious for sure.

113
00:09:30,830 --> 00:09:32,600
Then, he will definitely have me

114
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:36,600
bring men to capture and bring him to the Hall of Supreme Harmony for interrogation.

115
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:40,600
I will say that this Third Young Master Mei

116
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:46,400
did a few great deeds in Qingzhou, taking credit and becoming arrogant.

117
00:09:46,400 --> 00:09:49,800
However, his father was demoted and punished.

118
00:09:49,800 --> 00:09:54,000
He was very discontent from the beginning

119
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:56,000
and even gave birth to evil intentions,

120
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:58,800
openly attacking my guards.

121
00:09:58,800 --> 00:10:03,500
Eventually, I couldn't help but carry out a death sentence on the spot.

122
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:08,600
You are indeed wise, Your Highness.

123
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:14,200
It's just that, would the emperor think there are only verbal statements and no physical evidence?

124
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:16,400
All of my guards will witness it.

125
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:20,700
Besides, they are all associated with the Ninth Prince Manor.

126
00:10:20,700 --> 00:10:25,200
If that still doesn't work, then you can slash me with your sword.

127
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:28,200
I dare not. I dare not.

128
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:32,600
Look at how cowardly you are. If I take the sword to my body,

129
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:37,200
then it further proves that Third Young Master Mei attacked my guards.

130
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,600
I understand now

131
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:41,600
and ask that you give me orders.

132
00:10:47,550 --> 00:10:49,340
Master, General Mei is here.

133
00:10:49,340 --> 00:10:53,880
Mei Changyun, do you know you have committed a heinous crime?

134
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:57,320
I know my crimes and am willing to be punished.

135
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:59,510
How could you let this happen?

136
00:10:59,510 --> 00:11:02,410
Prince, I have never met the princess in the past.

137
00:11:02,410 --> 00:11:06,700
I only found out when I received your secret letter the day before.

138
00:11:08,840 --> 00:11:11,900
Forget it, forget it. The priority now

139
00:11:11,900 --> 00:11:14,190
is to find a solution to resolve this matter immediately.

140
00:11:14,190 --> 00:11:17,090
Prince, how do you want to resolve this?

141
00:11:17,090 --> 00:11:20,520
Have Yingyao and Shiqing marry according to the original plan

142
00:11:20,520 --> 00:11:22,940
and let this matter pass.

143
00:11:22,940 --> 00:11:27,320
Prince, I fear the children will not agree to this.

144
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,930
Are you senile?

145
00:11:28,930 --> 00:11:31,350
They have to go give thanks to His Majesty the day after tomorrow.

146
00:11:31,350 --> 00:11:34,890
Do you want them to defy imperial orders and be disrespectful? Do you have nine heads?

147
00:11:34,890 --> 00:11:37,360
Or do I have nine heads to be beheaded?

148
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:41,100
Prince, how could I dare to deceive the monarch? It's just...

149
00:11:41,100 --> 00:11:44,810
What? You don't want them to complete their marriage?

150
00:11:44,810 --> 00:11:46,980
I know my son Shiqing.

151
00:11:46,980 --> 00:11:48,950
He and Xiao Wanzi have great affection for each other.

152
00:11:48,950 --> 00:11:54,140
If we separate them now, they would rather die than live in hell.

153
00:11:54,730 --> 00:11:59,200
Would you not care for the well-being of the Mei family for a girl who performs on the street for a living?

154
00:11:59,200 --> 00:12:04,520
Since it has come to this stage, I have an idea.

155
00:12:04,520 --> 00:12:09,210
Speak. I will take Xiao Bao as my son. Then, he will be a member of the Mei family.

156
00:12:09,210 --> 00:12:13,630
Let him marry the princess. That way, this matter will be resolved.

157
00:12:24,060 --> 00:12:26,730
Listen to what you have just said.

158
00:12:26,730 --> 00:12:29,670
You are going to take a mountain bandit as your son

159
00:12:29,670 --> 00:12:31,640
and want my daughter to marry a mountain bandit?!

160
00:12:31,640 --> 00:12:34,290
Prince, this is the only way to resolve this matter.

161
00:12:34,290 --> 00:12:36,870
Prince, please grant this.

162
00:12:38,850 --> 00:12:43,190
I'm warning you. Don't oppose me.

163
00:12:59,410 --> 00:13:03,420
Do you know how serious of a crime you two have committed?

164
00:13:03,420 --> 00:13:06,660
Deceiving the monarch is not a child's game.

165
00:13:06,660 --> 00:13:09,310
I'm willing to bear the consequences.

166
00:13:09,310 --> 00:13:12,950
Please do not be angry, Father. It was not my intention to commit such a crime.

167
00:13:12,950 --> 00:13:16,120
It truly was a strange combination of circumstances and out of my control.

168
00:13:19,250 --> 00:13:22,450
The ones who deserve the death for their crimes are the mountains bandits who kidnapped you

169
00:13:22,450 --> 00:13:25,360
and that liar who impersonated a princess.

170
00:13:25,360 --> 00:13:29,030
It's a small matter to play tricks with the Ninth Prince Manor and General Manor.

171
00:13:29,030 --> 00:13:31,240
Deceiving the monarch is a serious matter!

172
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:34,260
These kinds of evil people should be sentenced to death immediately.

173
00:13:34,260 --> 00:13:38,390
Father, if you kill Xiao Bao, I won't want to live either.

174
00:13:38,390 --> 00:13:41,460
Xiao Wanzi and I will live and die together.

175
00:13:41,460 --> 00:13:44,240
Why are you both as muddle-headed as General Mei?

176
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:46,940
You are going to give thanks to His Majesty tomorrow.

177
00:13:46,940 --> 00:13:51,030
Father, why must you bitterly force me this way?

178
00:13:51,030 --> 00:13:54,510
Can you really bear to see me and Junior General regret for the rest of our lives?

179
00:13:54,510 --> 00:13:57,380
You are my biological father.

180
00:14:01,160 --> 00:14:04,690
Could it be that, from the start till the end,

181
00:14:04,690 --> 00:14:08,290
you really regard me as a tool for this manor?

182
00:14:17,760 --> 00:14:19,420
I know now.

183
00:14:23,250 --> 00:14:27,720
Speak. What must I do for you to spare Xiao Bao and Xiao Wanzi?

184
00:14:28,790 --> 00:14:30,720
As long as you both are willing to complete the marriage,

185
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:34,520
I can spare their lives.

186
00:14:36,460 --> 00:14:39,920
Fine. I promise you.

187
00:14:39,920 --> 00:14:41,740
I promise as well.

188
00:14:42,880 --> 00:14:45,830
All right. Go now.

189
00:14:52,950 --> 00:14:58,140
Prince, will you really spare that mountain bandit and girl?

190
00:14:58,140 --> 00:15:02,660
Now that it has come to this, what other solution is there?

191
00:15:03,610 --> 00:15:08,190
Prince, sparing them may bring troubles later on.

192
00:15:08,190 --> 00:15:12,210
After all, our princess was taken to their mountain fort.

193
00:15:12,210 --> 00:15:14,720
If outsiders know about this,

194
00:15:14,720 --> 00:15:18,430
how will our manor gain a foothold?

195
00:15:18,430 --> 00:15:20,530
Are you saying...

196
00:15:20,530 --> 00:15:25,620
Prince, the princess and prince consort are going to see His Majesty tomorrow.

197
00:15:25,620 --> 00:15:27,220
Why don't we...

198
00:15:28,690 --> 00:15:30,920
take care of them?

199
00:15:38,420 --> 00:15:41,390
[Thousands of Auspicious Gatherings]

200
00:15:41,390 --> 00:15:43,800
Princess, the carriage is ready.

201
00:15:43,800 --> 00:15:45,960
Why don't you go to the palace with Prince Consort together?

202
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:47,390
I have one more matter to attend to.

203
00:15:47,390 --> 00:15:49,160
I want to see Xiao Wanzi and Xiao Bao.

204
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:52,320
Princess, the auspicious time can't be delayed.

205
00:15:52,320 --> 00:15:55,030
I want to explain to them about Junior General and me,

206
00:15:55,030 --> 00:15:56,860
asking them to look at the bigger picture.

207
00:15:56,860 --> 00:16:00,430
I want them to know that I don't have a choice in certain matters.

208
00:16:00,430 --> 00:16:02,830
That way I can have them give up hope.

209
00:16:04,090 --> 00:16:06,850
Housekeeper Liu, you watched me grow up.

210
00:16:06,850 --> 00:16:08,820
You would let me say a few words to them, right?

211
00:16:08,820 --> 00:16:11,800
You are the prince's daughter and are filial.

212
00:16:11,800 --> 00:16:14,240
How could I not empathize with you?

213
00:16:15,060 --> 00:16:16,640
Escort the princess to the prison.

214
00:16:16,640 --> 00:16:18,040
Yes.

215
00:16:27,700 --> 00:16:29,090
- Xiao Bao.
- Yao Yao.

216
00:16:29,090 --> 00:16:30,350
Shiqing.

217
00:16:30,350 --> 00:16:32,860
Say, why did you two disappear in the morning?

218
00:16:32,860 --> 00:16:34,890
You are finally back.

219
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:38,000
Aren't I back?

220
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:42,760
Yao Yao, I didn't see you all morning. I missed you.

221
00:16:42,760 --> 00:16:44,960
Wait. Why are you two here?

222
00:16:44,960 --> 00:16:48,440
Did your father think it through and want to release us?

223
00:16:53,720 --> 00:16:56,830
My father wants to make use of the time when we are at the palace to harm you.

224
00:16:56,830 --> 00:16:59,230
We are here to save you.

225
00:17:00,620 --> 00:17:02,330
After we save you,

226
00:17:02,330 --> 00:17:05,630
I will settle you two into the home that my wet nurse left me.

227
00:17:05,630 --> 00:17:10,690
After we return from the palace, we will discuss what to do next.

228
00:17:13,330 --> 00:17:15,200
Is it just you? Where's the princess?

229
00:17:15,200 --> 00:17:16,740
Over there.

230
00:17:45,890 --> 00:17:47,640
Stop!

231
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:49,700
How bold of you, Third Young Master Mei. This is the Ninth Prince Manor.

232
00:17:49,700 --> 00:17:51,730
You are not allowed to behave wildly here.

233
00:17:51,730 --> 00:17:54,190
Princess, didn't you promise the prince?

234
00:17:54,190 --> 00:17:58,390
Housekeeper Li, I overheard your conversation with my father.

235
00:17:58,390 --> 00:18:00,970
Then, I won't be polite. Take them down.

236
00:18:25,160 --> 00:18:26,730
Leave this to me. Leave now.

237
00:18:26,730 --> 00:18:29,000
Yes. Let's go.

238
00:18:29,600 --> 00:18:32,580
General Mei, you have gone too far.

239
00:18:33,600 --> 00:18:35,560
Mei Changyun!

240
00:18:43,260 --> 00:18:45,800
You dare to create a ruckus at a prince's manor.

241
00:18:45,800 --> 00:18:48,260
Have you lost your mind?

242
00:18:48,870 --> 00:18:52,930
Prince, I have an important matter

243
00:18:52,930 --> 00:18:55,270
I want to report to you.

244
00:19:05,020 --> 00:19:07,120
This is the small home that I acquired for my wet nurse.

245
00:19:07,120 --> 00:19:10,300
She's now back in her hometown with her family.

246
00:19:10,300 --> 00:19:12,700
Thus, no one knows of this place.

247
00:19:12,700 --> 00:19:17,210
Xiao Bao, you and Xiao Wanzi can wait here.

248
00:19:17,210 --> 00:19:19,140
We must enter the palace to see His Majesty now.

249
00:19:19,140 --> 00:19:24,180
Wife, will it be safe for you two to enter the palace now?

250
00:19:24,180 --> 00:19:26,470
After all, you just released us.

251
00:19:26,470 --> 00:19:28,600
The prince is furious.

252
00:19:28,600 --> 00:19:31,480
What should we do if he tells His Majesty?

253
00:19:31,480 --> 00:19:34,190
That's right. There is General Mei, too.

254
00:19:34,190 --> 00:19:38,280
Will anything happen to him at the Ninth Prince Manor?

255
00:19:38,280 --> 00:19:41,820
Don't worry. My father regards keeping face as a life and death matter.

256
00:19:41,820 --> 00:19:46,750
He won't let anyone know that his daughter entered a mountain fort before.

257
00:19:46,750 --> 00:19:49,340
My father has an even more important matter to tend to.

258
00:19:49,340 --> 00:19:51,760
