267
00:20:44,630 --> 00:20:48,970
Smart. Smart.

268
00:20:48,970 --> 00:20:53,170
What a pity. What a pity.

269
00:20:53,170 --> 00:20:58,260
Thank you for your consideration. You are a great planner, Prince.

270
00:20:58,260 --> 00:21:03,030
You dispatched my father to Yongzhou and summoned us here to the capital.

271
00:21:03,030 --> 00:21:06,870
You came to this home that belonged to the princess's wet nurse so quickly.

272
00:21:06,870 --> 00:21:11,150
I am guessing that since we entered the capital, we were constantly being watched by you.

273
00:21:11,150 --> 00:21:15,980
You are very clear about my matters.

274
00:21:15,980 --> 00:21:19,350
I fear that I'm more clear of your matters than you think.

275
00:21:19,350 --> 00:21:23,720
Could it be that you can give me more surprises?

276
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:27,640
