282
00:21:42,860 --> 00:21:46,720
Saying that, aren't you afraid that others will hear?

283
00:21:49,000 --> 00:21:51,800
You all are people who are about to die anyway.

284
00:21:51,800 --> 00:21:54,690
It is of no worry for me to say these things to you.

285
00:21:54,690 --> 00:21:57,410
Sixth Prince, this is the capital.

286
00:21:57,420 --> 00:22:00,950
I was just about to enter the palace with Third Young Master Mei to thank His Majesty.

287
00:22:00,950 --> 00:22:04,120
If you do anything to us, His Majesty will never let you off.

288
00:22:04,120 --> 00:22:07,700
Moreover, he will also investigate why you are doing this.

289
00:22:07,700 --> 00:22:09,740
Say, Princess,

290
00:22:09,740 --> 00:22:12,530
